---------------
- Update Help -
---------------

1. Command Prompt Stuck at: "Updating Installation"

  a) Make sure these programs are closed:
	1. Command Prompt
	2. SRCDS.EXE
	3. Steam
  b) Make sure it is not being blocked by firewalls
  c) Is the program trusted?

2. Update Wont work at all?
   
  a) Try reinstalling to a new directory
     or deleting the old install files.